" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/nexas_logo.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/nexas_logo.png" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/nexas_logo.png" alt="" class="wp-image-123641"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：官网 © 2024 forCreators Pte Ltd.</figcaption></figure><p></p><p> NEXAS 是北美 forCreators Pte. Ltd（首席执行官：Harry So）运营的 VTuber 办公室，自称“虚拟人才学院”。 2023 年 12 月，我们宣布获得来自也投资了日本 VTuber 相关公司的投资者的资金。 2月23日，我们宣布NEXAS成立。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="NEXAS 宣传视频 #1" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pvxEuZYGRfs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow"><p> <a href="https://nexas.live/virtual-talent-academia-nexas-launched-by-forcreators-post-funding/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="forCreators完成天使轮融资并推出虚拟人才学院NEXAS">forCreators完成天使轮融资并推出虚拟人才学院NEXAS</a></p><cite>耐克斯</cite></blockquote><p></p><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">3天内27人首次亮相“AniLive”</h3><p>此次NEXAS，27位新人将在新兴的VTuber平台“ <strong>AniLive</strong> ”上首次亮相，为期三天。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AP1GczMHTppAVNdgRreyJFrb7vJwOpmWbZYpF8ukcxvrEtKTxOq51SIAGQsiIbva0SqloydQyHneiigcwpyO2VzkxxSfPpSt-C29qQ8UXruRewAmlJ3Eb5fy1ZEhc8X6SiSADchXdwBjHeqqyb68lvl-Kz2Y=w900-h1200-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：X（推特）<br> © 2024 forCreators 私人有限公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embe